Frank Zappa

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

follow me on Instagram, Youtube, Patreon and my website.

NOTE: Try to vote on the quality of the model/training an not based on how easily you are offended by the subject.

Frank Zappa

Suggested Weight: 1.0 - 1.2 (high weights work well)

Suggested prompts

  • photo of z4pp4:1.2 wearing a ((frog costume)), film grain, soul patch goatee, sharp focus, detailed face

  • adding "soul patch goatee" helps. Getting the "Zappa moustache" is a little trickier, I suggest adding "full moustache" to the prompt which will have mixed results

  • Weights higher than 1.0 seem to work well, 1.2 is a sweet spot.

Training

  • trained on ~16 images

  • Learning Rate: 0.005:1000, 0.001:2000, 0.0001:5000, 0.00005

  • Total Steps: 15,000

  • Batch Size: 1

  • Gradient Steps: 1
